    "description": "A Lone Piece is a single-player chess game with a twist. You are a single pawn destined to fight or flee the opposing pieces. This game is all about:<br><br>♟️  You against everyone. Outsmart all the other pieces <br>♟️  Eat them to get power-ups<br>♟️  Defeat the evil king<br>♟️  Endless amount of procedurally generated levels that get increasingly more difficult<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180920/extras/62724d241ed2c740d2d9332b85776323.poster.avif?t=1731052261\" width=600 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180920/extras/62724d241ed2c740d2d9332b85776323.webm?t=1731052261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180920/extras/62724d241ed2c740d2d9332b85776323.mp4?t=1731052261\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >♚ Opponents you know and love ♚</h2><br>♙ Pawn is a simple and predictable piece. <i>But you better watch out if it gets to the other side</i><br>♖ Rook is a defending powerhouse. There's no way of escaping when it's securing the exit<br>♘ There is unpredictable and then there is Knight<br>♗ With Bishop in the board, you have to be careful right from the start. They like to attack<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >♚ For everyone ♚ </h2><br>♕ Puzzles get increasingly harder based on your skills. Starts with 4x4 grid against one piece and gradually turns to full board and 16 pieces<br>♕ A good way to teach chess to children as well as mental workout for more adult taste<br>♕ Whether you're a seasoned chess player or a newcomer to the game, increasing difficulty makes sure you will have enough of a challenge<br>♕ Up your mental game? Checkmate<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180920/extras/a369b30085820be6b196cf1ba25cb97f.poster.avif?t=1731052261\" width=616 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180920/extras/a369b30085820be6b196cf1ba25cb97f.webm?t=1731052261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
